<%- include('./partials/head') %>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/sav.css?v=21">
<%- include('./partials/sidebar', { active: 'sav' }) %>

<main class="flex-1 sav-module" data-sav-token="<%= savApiToken %>">
  <div class="px-6 lg:px-10 py-8 max-w-3xl">

    <div class="mb-6">
      <div class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Intégrations</div>
      <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-500">Slack/Discord, Google Reviews, WhatsApp, Qonto</div>
    </div>

    <form id="sav-integrations-form" class="space-y-5">

      <section class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5">
        <h2 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">forum</span> Slack / Discord</h2>
        <div>
          <label class="block text-xs font-semibold text-slate-600 mb-1">Webhook URL (Slack ou Discord, format identique)</label>
          <input type="url" name="slackWebhookUrl" placeholder="https://hooks.slack.com/services/..." class="w-full rounded-xl border border-slate-300 px-3 py-2 text-sm">
        </div>
        <div class="mt-3">
          <label class="block text-xs font-semibold text-slate-600 mb-1">Canal (informationnel)</label>
          <input type="text" name="slackChannel" placeholder="#sav" class="w-full rounded-xl border border-slate-300 px-3 py-2 text-sm">
        </div>
        <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-500">Notifications envoyées : nouveau ticket, ticket assigné, SLA &lt; 24h, défaut produit confirmé, paiement 149 € reçu.</p>
        <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-slate-500">Slash command Slack : <code>/sav-prendre &lt;numero&gt;</code> → POST /api/sav/slack/command (header X-Slack-Secret).</p>
      </section>

      <section class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5">
        <h2 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">star</span> Google Reviews</h2>
        <div>
          <label class="block text-xs font-semibold text-slate-600 mb-1">URL Google Reviews CarPartsFrance</label>
          <input type="url" name="googleReviewsUrl" placeholder="https://g.page/r/..." class="w-full rounded-xl border border-slate-300 px-3 py-2 text-sm">
        </div>
        <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-500">Lien utilisé pour rediriger les clients qui notent ≥ 4/5 sur la page <code>/sav/feedback/[numero]</code>. Email J+7 envoyé automatiquement par le cron quotidien.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5">
        <h2 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">chat</span> WhatsApp Business</h2>
        <label class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm">
          <input type="checkbox" name="whatsappEnabled" class="rounded text-primary"> Activer le bouton "Envoyer dossier au fournisseur"
        </label>
        <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-slate-500">L'envoi réel nécessite les variables d'env <code>WHATSAPP_API_TOKEN</code> et <code>WHATSAPP_PHONE_ID</code>. Sinon le bouton génère un lien <code>wa.me</code> à ouvrir manuellement.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5">
        <h2 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">euro</span> Qonto (facturation 149 €)</h2>
        <label class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm">
          <input type="checkbox" name="qontoEnabled" class="rounded text-primary"> Activer la création automatique de facture Qonto
        </label>
        <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-slate-500">Variables d'env requises : <code>QONTO_API_LOGIN</code>, <code>QONTO_SECRET_KEY</code>, <code>QONTO_ORG_SLUG</code>, <code>QONTO_STAKEHOLDER_ID</code>. Sans ces clés, la facturation passe en mode "dev" (placeholder).</p>
      </section>

      <div class="flex justify-end">
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-base mr-1">save</span> Enregistrer</button>
      </div>

      <div id="sav-integrations-feedback" class="hidden rounded-xl border p-3 text-sm"></div>
    </form>
  </div>
</main>

<script src="/js/sav-admin.js?v=4" defer></script>
<%- include('./partials/footer') %>
